---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  current="about"
  title="About RRS Realty Group, Southeast Wisconsin Agent Matching"
  description="RRS Realty Group is a Southeast Wisconsin service that connects homeowners and buyers with vetted, licensed local real estate agents. Learn how and why we do it."
>
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">About us</p>
      <h1>Real Estate Help That Starts Local</h1>
      <p>RRS Realty Group exists to take the guesswork out of finding a great agent in Southeast Wisconsin.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:40px">
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Choosing a real estate agent is one of the biggest decisions in a move, and most people start it the hardest way possible, searching online, comparing strangers, and hoping the name they pick turns out to be the right one. The agent you choose shapes how your sale or purchase goes, how much money is on the table, and how stressful the whole thing feels.</p>
      <p>RRS Realty Group was built to make that first step easier, and personal. We partner with a team of trusted agents, but we don't drop your name into a queue for whoever picks it up first. A real person reaches out, has an actual conversation with you about your goals, and then connects you with the right agent and resources for your situation. Not a national call center. Not an out-of-town agent who's never set foot in your neighborhood. A tailored introduction to a real local professional who knows your market.</p>

      <h2>Why Local Matters Here</h2>
      <p>Southeast Wisconsin isn't one market, it's dozens. What sells a home in Wauwatosa is different from Cedarburg, which is different again from Kenosha or the lakefront. Pricing, timing, buyer expectations, even which improvements pay off all shift block to block. An agent who works your specific area brings knowledge that simply can't be faked from a distance, and that knowledge is what protects your money and your timeline.</p>

      <h2>How We Work</h2>
      <p>Our service is free for homeowners and buyers, and there's never any obligation. We make money the same way most referral services do, through the agents we partner with, which means it costs you nothing to get matched. You're free to ask questions, take your time, and decide whether to move forward entirely on your own terms.</p>

      <h2>Start With the Guides</h2>
      <p>We'd rather you make an informed decision than a rushed one. Our <a href="/guides/">local guides</a> answer the real questions Southeast Wisconsin homeowners and buyers ask, about pricing, timing, the selling process, and how to tell a good agent from a forgettable one. Read first, reach out when you're ready.</p>

      <div class="inline-cta">
        <h3>Ready When You Are</h3>
        <p>Get matched with a trusted local agent, free, no pressure.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/get-started/">Find my agent →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
